CREATE TABLE "cameras" (
	"id" varchar PRIMARY KEY NOT NULL,
	"serial_number" varchar DEFAULT '',
	"name" varchar DEFAULT '',
	"resolution" varchar DEFAULT '',
	"fps" integer DEFAULT 0,
	"data" json DEFAULT '{}'::json
);

CREATE TABLE "robots" (
	"id" varchar PRIMARY KEY NOT NULL,
	"serial_number" varchar DEFAULT '',
	"name" varchar DEFAULT '',
	"model" varchar DEFAULT '',
	"notes" text DEFAULT '',
	"data" json DEFAULT '{}'::json
);

CREATE TABLE "user_config" (
	"id" integer PRIMARY KEY GENERATED ALWAYS AS IDENTITY (sequence name "user_config_id_seq" INCREMENT BY 1 MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 2147483647 START WITH 1 CACHE 1),
	"user_id" uuid,
	"config" json DEFAULT '{}'::json
);

CREATE TABLE "robot_models" (
	"id" integer PRIMARY KEY GENERATED ALWAYS AS IDENTITY (sequence name "robot_models_id_seq" INCREMENT BY 1 MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 2147483647 START WITH 1 CACHE 1),
	"name" varchar NOT NULL,
	"dir_name" varchar NOT NULL,
	"class_name" varchar NOT NULL,
	"config_class_name" varchar NOT NULL,
	"properties" json DEFAULT '{}'::json
);
ALTER TABLE "cameras" ALTER COLUMN "id" SET DATA TYPE integer USING "id"::integer;
ALTER TABLE "cameras" ALTER COLUMN "id" ADD GENERATED ALWAYS AS IDENTITY (sequence name "cameras_id_seq" INCREMENT BY 1 MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 2147483647 START WITH 1 CACHE 1);
ALTER TABLE "robots" ALTER COLUMN "id" SET DATA TYPE integer USING "id"::integer;
ALTER TABLE "robots" ALTER COLUMN "id" ADD GENERATED ALWAYS AS IDENTITY (sequence name "robots_id_seq" INCREMENT BY 1 MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 2147483647 START WITH 1 CACHE 1);
